race.comment: ONLY THE BEST (2) turned in a terrific effort to win by 3.5 lengths this course and distance from the front, improving again. On a quick backup and will skip over again and run along. Nicely placed to score again. VITESSE BREEZE (1) was a determined winner two back then drifted back last time and finished 2 lengths in fourth and likely had an excuse. Has the rail today and is a decent chance to bounce. INCIVILITY (3) beat the above two back from the front and then disappointed last time. He's better than that and his best numbers would have him right in the finish. BLOWN AWAY (5) ran a better race last start and may have turned the corner. Keep onside.
